(secondQuint)Candesartan Cilexetil/Amlodipine Combination Tablets LD, HD Special Drug Use Surveillance "Hypertension: Long-Term Use".

 This special drug use surveillance was designed to investigate the safety and efficacy of long-term use of candesartan cilexetil/amlodipine combination tablets (Unisia Combination Tablets) in patients with hypertension in the routine clinical setting.

 The usual adult dosage is one tablet (8 mg/2.

5 mg or 8 mg/5 mg as candesartan cilexetil/amlodipine) administered orally once daily.

